# Host artifacts must never leak into the image: node_modules holds platform-specific
# binaries (built for Windows here, useless on Alpine), and dist is rebuilt inside.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage

# Secrets: the container gets env vars from compose, never a baked-in .env.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

.git
.github
.vscode
**/*.log
docs
